{"tid":572643,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無方法短時間改善到英文說話","createTime":"2018-02-25T17:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T08:58:54.000Z","uid":73066,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0aca23051ef81358dbe094d96f2ce26b5ac993","tid":572643,"uid":73066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"英文程度其實可以同外國人溝通（都聽得明7-8成）<br />\n當然係因為啲外國人就我英文程度咁講<br />\n但自己有時睇美劇睇戲唔較字幕去聽都聽得明<br />\n屌好似離左題，講講下去左聆聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實係咁，<br />\n因為黎緊要去航空公司見空少<br />\n但自己講英文好多時都係諗好個中文再轉成英文再諗下啲GRAMMER先講出黎<br />\n所以講野好慢，有時比唔到即時RESPONSE <br />\n搞到上次都見CX都衰左<br />\n而家都搵緊啲online platform or web for practising eng speaking<br />\n但有無巴絲有意見？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果今次再見衰有諗住出面報啲大型機構啲英文course ，因為中三報過一年englishtown, 都幾有用。由完全唔敢講英文去到果陣英文寫文可以錯0 grammer（雖然個sentence pattern 好簡單到中等水平），但主要因為有個會話班可以同鬼佬溝通，所以諗住報多次進修（如果再衰多次interview ）, 因為真係好想做空少 <br />\n巴絲有無建議？"},{"pid":"f7c5e3abba67d3edab68e19efee565a0f6164ea5","tid":572643,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"08101768c59e00e2077015d6ddfe4f01a1616d5e","tid":572643,"uid":73066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"做咩咁都要負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08b868278f42518bb447c964acfa3025eeb8d3f","tid":572643,"uid":73066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T18:46:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"47646f7c1c43c8fc828352c0e0e8ffbc196af397","tid":572643,"uid":105715,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T18:49:36.000Z","msg":"飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be7a1651a11a290e4b7f580acc80ae9bb6503e0","tid":572643,"uid":51174,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T18:50:12.000Z","msg":"其實鬼佬口講 根本唔會點理grammar <br />\n係寫字或者打出黎先會睇"},{"pid":"afe25cc6e91